title: Ebro In The Morning - RIP Biz Markie + Space Jam
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/19.

The crew talks about what Biz Markie meant to the world (22), and Ebro trolls about the new Space Jam (47), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (13:00 & 42) and we find out who played themselves (32).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
